{
  "text": "A type generated from the grammar in Table 2 is such that any recursive type : occurring in does not contain on the left of \u2192. This is a simpli\u00ffcation of the notion of positive type of [CITATION_1] . The fact that we only deal with a restricted form of types will be essential in the de\u00ffnition of subtyping.",
